p: \rGreetings.
\rThe slow snowfall gives a... tranquil feeling, does it not?
\rIt's quiet and serene... but in the heat of battle, it hardens to cold, destructive hail.
\rMy name is Yuki. \pn, is it?
\rI've been training for years with my Pokemon.
\rI'd wish you luck... but I don't want to waste my breath.
pbTrainerIntro(:ELITEFOUR_Hail)
$PokemonGlobal.nextBattleBack="Hail"
pbTrainerBattle(PBTrainers::ELITEFOUR_Hail,"Yuki",_I("Very nice. You battle eloquently."),false,0)
for poke in $Trainer.party
if poke.hp==0
$game_variables[170] = pbGet(170) - 1
end
end
\rWonderful. You battle with poise and grace.
\rCongratulations. The doors to our Champion should open, now that you've defeated the Elite Four.
\rBest of luck, challenger. You might need it.
\rWonderful. You battle with poise and grace.
\rI'm sure you can easily handle the rest of the Elite Four.
\rI wish you the best of luck, \pn.
pbTrainerEnd
$game_map.need_refresh=true
